				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A game feature few people use is "tab targeting".  Target your mob then hit tab once.  Now when you lose target from reclaim energy, you can hit tab twice while casting your new pet to retarget the mob and sic your new pet on it right as it is summoned.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
